<placeName cert="high">Oxyrhynchus</placeName></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">Ἅρ</unclear>παλος Ἡρᾶτι τῶι <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ἀδελ</unclear>φῷ 

    <lb n="2"/>χαίρειν. 

    <lb n="3"/>ἔγραψ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear> <gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> διὰ Ἡρακλείδ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ου</supplied> <gap extent="4" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="unknown" reason="lost" unit="character"/> 

    <lb n="4"/>τα τῆς <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ο</supplied>ἰκονομίας σου· συνέδησα 

    <lb n="5"/>ἐπιστ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>λήν μου καὶ ἄλλην τοῦ ἐν-

    <lb n="6"/>θάδε νομικοῦ πρὸς τὸν παρὰ σοὶ 

    <lb n="7"/>νομικόν. ἐκομισάμην παρὰ Ἀμ-

    <lb n="8"/>μων<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ίο</supplied>υ τὰ πεμφθέντα <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">μοι. ἔπ</supplied><unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">εμ</unclear>-

    <lb n="9"/>ψα δέ σοι δι᾽ αὐτοῦ κνίδιν γάρου χρηστοῦ, 

    <lb n="10"/><choice><corr>λαβόντος</corr><sic>λαβων</sic></choice> παρ᾽ ἐμοῦ εἰς λόγον ναύλου 

    <lb n="11"/>καὶ φ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>ρέτρου <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="6">ϛ</num>. τὸ ἐπιστόλιον τὸ 

    <lb n="12"/>τῆς ἐπιθήκης τὸ διαπεμφθέν σοι ἀπ᾽ Ἀ-

    <lb n="13"/>λεξα<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">νδ</unclear>ρείας διὰ ἀσφαλοῦς μοι πέμψον. 

    <lb n="14"/>ἐκομ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ι</supplied>σάμην παρὰ Ἡρακλείδου <choice><corr>σπάθι-

    <lb n="15"/>ον</corr><sic>σπατιον</sic></choice> οἴν<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ο</unclear>υ. καὶ μὴ βαροῦ. οὗτινος γὰρ 

    <lb n="16"/>ἐὰν χρείαν σχῶ, γράψω σοι. ἐγράφη μοι 

    <lb n="17"/>ἀπὸ Ὀά<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">σ</supplied>εως ὑπὸ Λεωνίδου ὡς τοῦ φίλου 

    <lb n="18"/>μεταβαλόντος αὐτῷ τὴν τιμὴν τῶν δερμά-

    <lb n="19"/>των. ἐξέτασον <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">πα</supplied>ρὰ σοὶ πόσον αὐτῷ με-

    <lb n="20"/>τεβάλετο εἰς τὸν λόγον μου. καὶ ἐρε<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ῖς</supplied> 

    <lb n="21"/>Πατρ<gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="lost" unit="character"/><gap extent="1" reason="illegible" unit="character"/> <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">τ</unclear>ι ὅτι Ἡρακλείδης <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οὐ</supplied>δέν <unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">μ</unclear><supplied cert="high" reason="lost">οι</supplied> 

    <lb n="22"/><choice><corr>ὀφείλει</corr><sic>οφει<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">λ</unclear>ι</sic></choice> ἀπὸ λόγου τῆς μεγάλης Ὀάσεως 

    <lb n="23"/>καὶ οὐκ ἐχρῆν τὸν κάμηλον κατασχεῖν. 

    <lb n="24"/>ἐγὼ γὰρ <choice><corr>μιμούμενος</corr><sic>μειμουμενος</sic></choice> <choice><corr>ἐμαυτὸν</corr><sic>εματον</sic></choice> μέχρι 

    <lb n="25"/>τούτου οὐδὲν ἔπραξα, καὶ μέχρι τούτου 

    <lb n="26"/>ἤτω. τὰς γὰρ <expan><ex cert="high">δραχμὰς</ex></expan> <num value="1000">Α</num>, ἃς μετεβάλετο ὁ Ἡ-

    <lb n="27"/>ρακλείδης τοῖς αὑτοῦ ἐν τῇ μεγάλῃ 

    <lb n="28"/>Ὀάσι, ταύτας ἔσχεν ἐν τῷ Ὀξυρυγχείτῃ 

    <lb n="29"/><choice><corr>καὶ ἐμοὶ</corr><sic>καμοι</sic></choice> μετεβάλετο ἐν τῷ αὐτῷ Ὀξυ-

    <lb n="30"/>ρυγχείτῃ ὀφειλομένας μοι ὑπ᾽ αὐτοῦ. 

    <lb n="31"/>εἰκῇ οὖν κατεῖχον τὸν κάμηλον. 

    <lb n="32"/>πάντα μεταδώσεις αὐτῷ. περὶ ὧν β<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ού</supplied>-

    <lb n="33"/>λει, ἀνόκνως μοι γράφε. 

    <lb n="34"/><handShift new="m2"/> ἐρρῶσθ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αί σε</supplied> 

    <lb n="35"/>εὔχομ<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">αι</supplied> 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="37"/>Ἡρᾶτι <expan>π<ex cert="high">αρὰ</ex></expan> <choice><corr>Ἁρπάλου</corr><sic>αρπα<g type="x"/>λου</sic></choice> τοῦ ἀδελφοῦ. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.26863" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.26863" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="300" notBefore="101" type="textDate">II - III</date></p></div><div n="meta.26863" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Oxy.</title><biblScope type="volume">41</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">2983</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">26863</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0181</series>; <biblScope type="volume">41</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">2983</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0181;41;2983" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.26863" part="N" subtype="corrections" type="bibliography"><head>BL-Einträge nach BL-Konkordanz</head><bibl type="BL"><biblScope type="volume">VIII</biblScope>, S. <biblScope type="pages">264</biblScope></bibl></div><div n="meta.26863" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.26863" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p><placeName cert="high" type="ancientFindspot">Oxyrhynchos</placeName></p></div><div n="meta.26863" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://163.1.169.40/cgi-bin/library?e=d-000-00---0POxy--00-0-0-0prompt-10---4---Document---0-1l--1-en-50---20-about---001-001-1-0utfZz-8-00031-001-1-0utfZz-8-00&amp;a=d&amp;c=POxy&amp;cl=CL5.1.14&amp;d=HASH01ca2ef6972db272f5006c0f"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>